    <title>Matplotlib Markers 完整指南</title>
    <link href="https://blog.halunhaku.top/2025/07/16/matplotlib_markers/"/>
    <id>https://blog.halunhaku.top/2025/07/16/matplotlib_markers/</id>
    <published>2025-07-16T14:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-07-16T14:26:57.564Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Matplotlib-Markers-完整指南"><a href="#Matplotlib-Markers-完整指南" class="headerlink" title="Matplotlib Markers 完整指南"></a>Matplotlib Markers 完整指南</h1><h2 id="简介"><a href="#简介" class="headerlink" title="简介"></a>简介</h2><p>Matplotlib 中的 markers（标记）是数据可视化中的重要组成部分，用于在图表中标识数据点。markers 功能广泛应用于 <code>plot()</code>、<code>scatter()</code> 和 <code>errorbar()</code> 等函数中，帮助用户创建更直观、更具表现力的图表。</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="基本-Markers-列表"><a href="#基本-Markers-列表" class="headerlink" title="基本 Markers 列表"></a>基本 Markers 列表</h2><h3 id="点和形状标记"><a href="#点和形状标记" class="headerlink" title="点和形状标记"></a>点和形状标记</h3><table><thead><tr><th>标记符号</th><th>描述</th><th>用法示例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>.</code></td><td>点 (point)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;.&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>,</code></td><td>像素 (pixel)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;,&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>o</code></td><td>圆形 (circle)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;o&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>s</code></td><td>正方形 (square)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;s&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>D</code></td><td>菱形 (diamond)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;D&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>d</code></td><td>细菱形 (thin_diamond)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;d&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>p</code></td><td>五边形 (pentagon)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;p&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>8</code></td><td>八边形 (octagon)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;8&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>h</code></td><td>六边形1 (hexagon1)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;h&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>H</code></td><td>六边形2 (hexagon2)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;H&#39;)</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="三角形标记"><a href="#三角形标记" class="headerlink" title="三角形标记"></a>三角形标记</h3><table><thead><tr><th>标记符号</th><th>描述</th><th>用法示例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>^</code></td><td>上三角形 (triangle_up)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;^&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>v</code></td><td>下三角形 (triangle_down)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;v&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>&lt;</code></td><td>左三角形 (triangle_left)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;&lt;&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>&gt;</code></td><td>右三角形 (triangle_right)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;&gt;&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>1</code></td><td>下三角 (tri_down)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;1&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>2</code></td><td>上三角 (tri_up)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;2&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>3</code></td><td>左三角 (tri_left)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;3&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>4</code></td><td>右三角 (tri_right)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;4&#39;)</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="线条和符号标记"><a href="#线条和符号标记" class="headerlink" title="线条和符号标记"></a>线条和符号标记</h3><table><thead><tr><th>标记符号</th><th>描述</th><th>用法示例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>+</code></td><td>加号 (plus)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;+&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>x</code></td><td>叉号 (x)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;x&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>X</code></td><td>填充叉号 (x filled)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;X&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>*</code></td><td>星号 (star)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;*&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>P</code></td><td>填充加号 (plus filled)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;P&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td>&#96;</td><td>&#96;</td><td>竖线 (vline)</td></tr><tr><td><code>_</code></td><td>横线 (hline)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;_&#39;)</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="刻度标记"><a href="#刻度标记" class="headerlink" title="刻度标记"></a>刻度标记</h3><table><thead><tr><th>标记符号</th><th>描述</th><th>用法示例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>0</code></td><td>左刻度 (tickleft)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;0&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>1</code></td><td>右刻度 (tickright)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;1&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>2</code></td><td>上刻度 (tickup)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;2&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>3</code></td><td>下刻度 (tickdown)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;3&#39;)</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="插入符号标记"><a href="#插入符号标记" class="headerlink" title="插入符号标记"></a>插入符号标记</h3><table><thead><tr><th>标记符号</th><th>描述</th><th>用法示例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>4</code></td><td>左插入符 (caretleft)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;4&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>5</code></td><td>右插入符 (caretright)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;5&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>6</code></td><td>上插入符 (caretup)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;6&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>7</code></td><td>下插入符 (caretdown)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;7&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>8</code></td><td>左插入符（底部居中）</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;8&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>9</code></td><td>右插入符（底部居中）</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;9&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>10</code></td><td>上插入符（底部居中）</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;10&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>11</code></td><td>下插入符（底部居中）</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;11&#39;)</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="特殊标记"><a href="#特殊标记" class="headerlink" title="特殊标记"></a>特殊标记</h3><table><thead><tr><th>标记符号</th><th>描述</th><th>用法示例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>&#39;&#39;</code> 或 <code>&#39; &#39;</code></td><td>无标记 (nothing)</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;&#39;)</code></td></tr><tr><td><code>&#39;$...$&#39;</code></td><td>数学文本渲染</td><td><code>plt.plot(x, y, marker=&#39;$\u266B$&#39;)</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="高级-Markers-功能"><a href="#高级-Markers-功能" class="headerlink" title="高级 Markers 功能"></a>高级 Markers 功能</h2><h3 id="自定义路径标记"><a href="#自定义路径标记" class="headerlink" title="自定义路径标记"></a>自定义路径标记</h3><p>可以使用 <code>(x, y)</code> 坐标对的列表来定义自定义路径标记：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="keyword">as</span> plt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义自定义标记路径</span></span><br><span class="line">custom_marker = [(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>), (<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>), (<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">1</span>), (<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>), (<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">x = np.linspace(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = np.sin(x)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y, marker=custom_marker, markersize=<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.show()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="正多边形标记"><a href="#正多边形标记" class="headerlink" title="正多边形标记"></a>正多边形标记</h3><p>使用 <code>(numsides, style, angle)</code> 格式创建正多边形：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建一个六边形标记</span></span><br><span class="line">hexagon_marker = (<span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)  <span class="comment"># 6边形，样式0，角度0</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y, marker=hexagon_marker, markersize=<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="星形标记"><a href="#星形标记" class="headerlink" title="星形标记"></a>星形标记</h3><p>使用 <code>(numsides, style, angle)</code> 格式创建星形：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建一个五角星</span></span><br><span class="line">star_marker = (<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)  <span class="comment"># 5边形，样式1（星形），角度0</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y, marker=star_marker, markersize=<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="星号标记"><a href="#星号标记" class="headerlink" title="星号标记"></a>星号标记</h3><p>使用 <code>(numsides, style, angle)</code> 格式创建星号：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建一个8角星号</span></span><br><span class="line">asterisk_marker = (<span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)  <span class="comment"># 8边形，样式2（星号），角度0</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y, marker=asterisk_marker, markersize=<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="STIX-数学字体符号"><a href="#STIX-数学字体符号" class="headerlink" title="STIX 数学字体符号"></a>STIX 数学字体符号</h2><p>Matplotlib 支持使用 STIX 数学字体来创建特殊符号标记：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用音符符号作为标记</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y, marker=<span class="string">r&#x27;$\u266B$&#x27;</span>, markersize=<span class="number">15</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用希腊字母</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y, marker=<span class="string">r&#x27;$\alpha$&#x27;</span>, markersize=<span class="number">15</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 使用数学符号</span></span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y, marker=<span class="string">r&#x27;$\infty$&#x27;</span>, markersize=<span class="number">15</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="数字标记对照"><a href="#数字标记对照" class="headerlink" title="数字标记对照"></a>数字标记对照</h2><p>整数 0-11 对应特定的线条和三角形标记：</p><table><thead><tr><th>数字</th><th>对应标记</th><th>常量名</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>0</td><td>左刻度</td><td><code>TICKLEFT</code></td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>右刻度</td><td><code>TICKRIGHT</code></td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>上刻度</td><td><code>TICKUP</code></td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>下刻度</td><td><code>TICKDOWN</code></td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>左插入符</td><td><code>CARETLEFT</code></td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>右插入符</td><td><code>CARETRIGHT</code></td></tr><tr><td>6</td><td>上插入符</td><td><code>CARETUP</code></td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>下插入符</td><td><code>CARETDOWN</code></td></tr><tr><td>8</td><td>左插入符（底部居中）</td><td><code>CARETLEFTBASE</code></td></tr><tr><td>9</td><td>右插入符（底部居中）</td><td><code>CARETRIGHTBASE</code></td></tr><tr><td>10</td><td>上插入符（底部居中）</td><td><code>CARETUPBASE</code></td></tr><tr><td>11</td><td>下插入符（底部居中）</td><td><code>CARETDOWNBASE</code></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="MarkerStyle-类"><a href="#MarkerStyle-类" class="headerlink" title="MarkerStyle 类"></a>MarkerStyle 类</h2><p><code>MarkerStyle</code> 类提供了更高级的标记自定义功能：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> matplotlib.markers <span class="keyword">import</span> MarkerStyle</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.transforms <span class="keyword">as</span> transforms</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 创建自定义标记样式</span></span><br><span class="line">marker_style = MarkerStyle(<span class="string">&#x27;o&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 应用变换（旋转、偏移）</span></span><br><span class="line">transform = transforms.Affine2D().rotate_deg(<span class="number">45</span>)</span><br><span class="line">marker_style.set_transform(transform)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y, marker=marker_style, markersize=<span class="number">10</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="实用示例"><a href="#实用示例" class="headerlink" title="实用示例"></a>实用示例</h2><h3 id="基本用法"><a href="#基本用法" class="headerlink" title="基本用法"></a>基本用法</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="keyword">as</span> plt</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">x = np.linspace(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">10</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y1 = np.sin(x)</span><br><span class="line">y2 = np.cos(x)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">6</span>))</span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y1, marker=<span class="string">&#x27;o&#x27;</span>, label=<span class="string">&#x27;sin(x)&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.plot(x, y2, marker=<span class="string">&#x27;s&#x27;</span>, label=<span class="string">&#x27;cos(x)&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.legend()</span><br><span class="line">plt.grid(<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.show()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="散点图中的标记"><a href="#散点图中的标记" class="headerlink" title="散点图中的标记"></a>散点图中的标记</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 生成随机数据</span></span><br><span class="line">np.random.seed(<span class="number">42</span>)</span><br><span class="line">x = np.random.randn(<span class="number">100</span>)</span><br><span class="line">y = np.random.randn(<span class="number">100</span>)</span><br><span class="line">colors = np.random.rand(<span class="number">100</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">8</span>, <span class="number">6</span>))</span><br><span class="line">plt.scatter(x, y, c=colors, marker=<span class="string">&#x27;D&#x27;</span>, s=<span class="number">50</span>, alpha=<span class="number">0.7</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.colorbar()</span><br><span class="line">plt.title(<span class="string">&#x27;散点图示例&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.show()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="多种标记组合"><a href="#多种标记组合" class="headerlink" title="多种标记组合"></a>多种标记组合</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">markers = [<span class="string">&#x27;o&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;s&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;^&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;D&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;v&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;&lt;&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;&gt;&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;p&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;*&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;h&#x27;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">colors = plt.cm.tab10(np.linspace(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>, <span class="built_in">len</span>(markers)))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plt.figure(figsize=(<span class="number">12</span>, <span class="number">8</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i, (marker, color) <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">enumerate</span>(<span class="built_in">zip</span>(markers, colors)):</span><br><span class="line">    y = np.sin(x + i * <span class="number">0.3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    plt.plot(x, y, marker=marker, color=color, </span><br><span class="line">             label=<span class="string">f&#x27;marker: <span class="subst">&#123;marker&#125;</span>&#x27;</span>, markersize=<span class="number">8</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">plt.legend()</span><br><span class="line">plt.grid(<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.title(<span class="string">&#x27;多种标记示例&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">plt.show()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="注意事项"><a href="#注意事项" class="headerlink" title="注意事项"></a>注意事项</h2><ol><li><strong>性能考虑</strong>：在处理大量数据点时，复杂的标记可能会影响渲染性能</li><li><strong>可读性</strong>：选择标记时要考虑图表的可读性和美观性</li><li><strong>兼容性</strong>：某些标记在不同的后端可能显示效果不同</li><li><strong>大小调整</strong>：使用 <code>markersize</code> 参数调整标记大小以适应图表需求</li></ol><h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>Matplotlib 提供了丰富的标记选项，从简单的几何形状到复杂的自定义路径和数学符号。掌握这些标记的使用方法，可以帮助您创建更具表现力和专业性的数据可视化图表。选择合适的标记不仅能提高图表的可读性，还能增强数据的视觉表现力。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;Matplotlib-Markers-完整指南&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Matplotlib-Markers-完整指南&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Matplotlib Markers 完整指南&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Matplotlib Markers 完整指南&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;简介&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#简介&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;简介&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;简介&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Matplotlib 中的 markers（标记）是数据可视化中的重要组成部分，用于在图表中标识数据点。markers 功能广泛应用于 &lt;code&gt;plot()&lt;/code&gt;、&lt;code&gt;scatter()&lt;/code&gt; 和 &lt;code&gt;errorbar()&lt;/code&gt; 等函数中，帮助用户创建更直观、更具表现力的图表。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
